# Unofficial Cursor News â€” Feed Service Plan (Phases 1â€“7)

Build the **Unofficial Cursor News** app feed service through **vertical slices** (shippable user value per phase) and **modularity** (single-responsibility modules inside each slice).

**Product name:** Unofficial Cursor News  
**Positioning:** Unofficial fan app â€” **not affiliated with Anysphere.**  
**Brand copy:** Refer to the product as **Cursor** (not "Cursor AI").  
**Stack:** `api` (Node ingest + JSON API) + `mobile` (Expo Dev Client). Optional `web/` for browser preview.

**Out of scope:** Phase 8 (native Swift/iOS without Expo) â€” do not plan or implement unless user explicitly requests.

