**Do not:** paywall news; external payment CTAs that violate store rules without IAP where required.

---

## Phase 7 â€” Ship web + PWA

**Vertical slice:** Public URL; add-to-home-screen; production API.

**Work:** Deploy API (Railway/Fly/Render/etc.); deploy Expo EAS or static `web/` build (Netlify/Vercel); env-based `API_BASE`; PWA manifest + service worker shell; Privacy Policy + DMCA/opt-out page.

**Done when:** Public URL works on phone browser; ingest runs on schedule in production; disclaimer + attribution on every item.

**Do not:** go live without privacy/DMCA pages; expose scrape API keys client-side.

